				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Player interacts with the second mural of the Mausoleum puzzle and get the second piece of the story. This mural depicts Ketheric Thorm mourning at the tomb of his daughter (Isobel, though this is not revealed by the mural). The player's comment varies, depending on if they've met Ketheric or not."
